🌐 Project Name: Crypto Trackr
A live dashboard to track crypto portfolio, simulate investment, and manage wallet data.

🧠 What is it?
Ye ek React-based frontend dashboard hai jisme:

Apka crypto portfolio dikhaya jaata hai

Live prices CoinGecko API se fetch kiye jaate hain

Aap alert laga sakte ho kisi coin ke target price pe

Transaction history dikhata hai

Wallet sync aur download option bhi hai

DCA simulator bhi diya gaya hai (Dollar Cost Averaging)

🧩 Dashboard Components Breakdown:
✅ useState, useEffect, axios
Used to handle data, API calls, and updates in the UI.

🧾 Headings and Their Purpose:
1. 🏷️ Live Prices
Ye CoinGecko se har 5 minute me live prices fetch karta hai.

Aapke portfolio coins ka current value update hota rehta hai.

Use: Real-time tracking of your assets.

2. 📊 Your Portfolio
Ek table hai jo dikhaata hai:

Coin name & logo

Quantity (kitna coin hold karte ho)

Current price (live)

Total value (quantity × price)

Profit/Loss (aaj ka)

View Chart (last 7 days ka graph)

✅ Ye table automatic calculate karta hai total value aur profit.

3. 📈 7-Day Price Chart
Jab aap "View Chart" button click karte ho, wo coin ka 7 din ka price chart dikhata hai.

Use: Recent trend dekhne ke liye.

4. 🧮 Summary Cards
3 summary cards top pe:

Total Portfolio Value

Total Assets (kitne coins portfolio me hain)

Today’s Profit/Loss

✅ Gives you a quick overview in 1 second.

5. 🧠 DCA Simulator
DCA = Dollar Cost Averaging.

Ye tool simulate karta hai agar aap regular interval pe (monthly) investment karte to aaj ka value kya hota.

Inputs:

Coin

Investment per month

Kitne months

Output:

Total coins

Total invested

Current value

Profit / Loss

✅ Help karta hai strategy test karne me.

6. 📱 Wallet Sync
External wallet ko connect karke crypto data fetch kar sakte ho.

Note: Backend ya wallet API pe depend karta hai.

7. 🚨 Set Alerts
Aap manually kisi coin pe target price set kar sakte ho.

Jab price us target tak pahunchta hai, browser notification aur toast alert show hota hai.

✅ Useful for price tracking without checking again & again.

8. 📜 Transaction History
Dummy ya actual past transactions dikhata hai.

Portfolio based history create karta hai.

Use: Transparency and monitoring.

9. 📥 Download
Portfolio ka Excel ya JSON data download karne ka feature (via Download.js).

Useful for offline tracking ya presentation.

🔒 Logout Button
User authentication ke liye localStorage me user ID save hoti hai.

Logout button localStorage.clear() karta hai and user ko login page pe redirect karta hai.